## TL;DR
**Connector Trainer** is live for everyone in Falowen. It helps you link ideas with the right German connectors‚Äî**und, aber, denn, weil, deshalb, obwohl, dass, wenn** and more‚Äîusing **English explanations + German examples** and **instant tips**. No scoring, only **learning mode** so you can focus on clarity and word order.

